  "description": "sweepDirection at full negative — the pitch bends slowly downward across the entire 7-second decay. With pitchLock off and minimal snap intensity, a gentle tap becomes a falling star: the tone drifts from its struck pitch toward the abyss. DEPTH macro controls how far into darkness the descent reaches. feliX at its most atmospheric.",
